). A diterpenoid ( 436 ) showed significant P-glycoprotein inhibitory activity compared with the positive control (cyclosporine A) (
). Compound 404 exhibited remarkable multidrug resistance regulation at 20 μM (
). Two jatrophane-type diterpenoids (
297 – 298
